body_html: Feel free to file as a bug/request at the TensorFlow Serving link from @reedwm. Note that this looks like more general compiler / bazel issue that the team will likely not have time to investigate. If you do find a resolution, please share it along with any PRs for documentation or build changes. Thanks!
